---
title: Hazelnut Crusted Salmon with pan-fried asparagus
description: Asparagus is a vegetable that can be tricky to get right, but a combination of searing and steaming in this recipe ensures it's flavourful and just cooked enough. The garlicky mashed potatoes and hazelnut crumb are other little touches that make this dish extra special.
